<div class="container-fluid heroguidepage no-subhead">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12">
        <h1>Using Logflare in your Event Analytics Pipeline</h1>
        <p>Send Logflare arbitrary events and event metadata.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="miniimgbox">
    <img src="/images/marketing/guides/bigquerylogo.png" alt="">
