        <div class="cont">
          <h1 class="menu1cont" id="event-analytics">Event Analytics</h1>
          <p>Use Logflare as the hub of your event analytics pipeline. Send Logflare arbitrary events with arbitrary dynamic metadata. Logflare handles inserting into BigQuery and updating the underlying schema. It's the easiest way on the market to stream data into a BigQuery data warehouse.</p>
          <h2 id="demo-video">Demo Video</h2>
          <p>Here we send Logflare arbitrary events via a POST request, and query them immediately in realtime.</p>
          <div class="minimg">
            <div style="position: relative; padding-bottom: 62.5%; height: 0;"><iframe src="https://www.loom.com/embed/d0c58ce170c24af0be6c22bc6fb0d6f4" frameborder="0" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;"></iframe></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
